The pre-print can be found here: https://doi.org/10.31234/osf.io/wp73u
The analysis codes, results, and figures can be found on OSF: https://osf.io/r93es. 

The main folder contains the raw EEG data in standard bids format.  

For codes, results, & figures, see OSF: Moerel, D., Grootswagers, T., Robinson, A. K., Engeler, P., Holcombe, A. O., & Carlson, T. A. (2026, April 14). Rotation-tolerant representations elucidate the time course of high-level object processing. https://doi.org/10.17605/OSF.IO/R93ES